{
  "texts": [
    "[139], a real-time anomaly data detection method is proposed for safe driving based on the driver's emotional state and the cooperative vehicular networks.",
    "Zhang et al. [140] proposed a safety-oriented vehicular controller area network (SOVCAN) based on driver emotion detection.",
    "The architecture of SOVCAN consists of a data acquisition layer, an intra-net layer, and an inter-net layer.",
    "At the data acquisition layer, the driver's physiological and psychological data are collected by the in-car mobile.",
    "At the intra-net layer, the data is transmitted to the on-board device for emotion perception."
  ]
}